flowchart TD
    Start([New Milestone]) --> SDD

    subgraph SDD[SDD - Specification Driven Development]
        S1[Write ADRs]
        S2[Write Feature Specs]
        S3[Create Diagrams]
        S4[Peer Review]
        S1 --> S2 --> S3 --> S4
    end

    SDD --> Gate1{Gate 1:<br/>Complete?<br/>No TODOs?}
    Gate1 -->|No| SDD
    Gate1 -->|Yes| Next([→ BDD Phase])

    style SDD   fill:#e1f5ff
    style Start fill:#f5f5f5
    style Next  fill:#f5f5f5
